summary: This is a retexture of the Temptress Armor. I did not create the meshes for this to work.
descriptionHtml:
As stated above this is a retexture of the Temptress Armor, specifically the shirt and shorts. I did not create the meshes for this to work, nor did I create any of the other textures that are in this mod. I left the rest of the Temptress armor in, and did not retexture anything but the shirt and shorts. This mod CANNOT be used alongside the Temptress SHIRT, OR SHORTS. All you need to do is copy over all the original Temptress files and youre done. Note the boots and cape are NOT INCLUDED. Get the boots here, http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=130717922 the cape is located here,http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12092/? The Flying is also NOT INCLUDED. Locate it here, http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/15775/? If anyone needs help installing the flying mod check out my video here, http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TlC_V6LMfB8 Big shoutout to DE4TH R3B0RN for helping me with the retexture. Couldn't have done this without him.

The Armor is under Ebony titled Temptress Shirt, and Temptress Shorts.
author: samueladams017
